The Heart Behind the Hearth

Meet Kelly

Garnet Hearth was born from the understanding that motherhood transforms us and that transformation deserves support.

Whether you're a first-time mom wondering where "you" went, a stepmom navigating complex family dynamics, or simply a woman seeking a moment to exhale... this space was created with you in mind.

No pretense. No agenda. Just genuine care, holistic practices, and a warm place to land.
